        <!-- Conclusion Text -->
        <div class="assessments-conclusion-section-text">
            <h2>How is a Psychological Evaluation Helpful?</h2>
            <p>
                Psychological evaluations can be beneficial to determine appropriate diagnoses that may benefit from treatment. Evaluations provide resources and recommendations even if no diagnosis is supported by the results. They offer valuable information about strengths, areas for growth, and recommendations to enhance processing skills.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>